            "synopsis" : {"type" : 23, "value" : "After the lanceboard game (HAV_MolsDeal_Lanceboard_ThreeWay.lsj), Mol will slink off away from Raphael and can be spoken to alone to discuss his deal. This dialogue can happen as long as the inn has not been attacked yet.\r\n\r\nAfter the game with Raphael, Mol can be found in a corner by a dusty shelf, where she's shoved the lanceboard. She clearly stole a piece from the set, fiddling with it as the player approaches."},
